      <title>华尔街银行受投资银行业务收益推动</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/wall-street-banks-propelled-by-investment-banking-gains-2024-10-15/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华尔街最大的几家银行报告称，第三季度投资银行费用有所上升，这得益于交易的增多和公司发行债务的增多，这些银行还表示，它们的新活动渠道看起来很健康——尽管一些领域的复苏速度较慢。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/wall-street-banks-propelled-by-investment-banking-gains-2024-10-15/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 14:05:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>渣打银行欢迎英国法院就 Libor 替代利率作出“明确”裁决</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/stanchart-partially-wins-uk-court-case-over-replacement-rate-libor-2024-10-15/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[渣打银行周二在伦敦一家法院赢得了一项竞标，以取代其用于设定部分股票股息利率的金融基准，该银行表示，此举为 Libor 的替代利率提供了“清晰度”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/stanchart-partially-wins-uk-court-case-over-replacement-rate-libor-2024-10-15/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 13:34:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>PNC Financial 季度利润因利息收入减少和拨备增加而下降</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/pnc-financial-quarterly-profit-drops-lower-interest-income-higher-provisions-2024-10-15/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[PNC金融公司周二公布第三季度净利润下降4%，原因是该公司从客户利息支付中获得的收益减少，并拨出更大的资本缓冲来弥补在不确定的经济形势下可能无法偿还的贷款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/pnc-financial-quarterly-profit-drops-lower-interest-income-higher-provisions-2024-10-15/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 13:30:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>花旗集团利润超出预期，投资银行业务激增</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/citigroup-profit-drops-bigger-stockpiles-potential-loan-losses-2024-10-15/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[花旗集团第三季度利润降幅小于预期，得益于投资银行业务（尤其是债务承销业务）的收益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/citigroup-profit-drops-bigger-stockpiles-potential-loan-losses-2024-10-15/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 12:08:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛利润超出预期，因债券销售推动投资银行业务</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/goldman-sachs-profit-jumps-45-investment-banking-strength-2024-10-15/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受债券销售、股票发行和并购活动反弹的推动，高盛第三季度利润超出预期，其股价周二上涨逾 3%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/goldman-sachs-profit-jumps-45-investment-banking-strength-2024-10-15/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 11:27:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国银行利润超出预期，投资银行业务和交易实力强劲</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/bofa-profit-drops-weaker-interest-income-2024-10-15/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行第三季度利润下降，因为它向客户支付了更多费用以保留他们的存款，但受投资银行和交易业务强劲推动，该行盈利超出预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/bofa-profit-drops-weaker-interest-income-2024-10-15/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 10:46:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国监管机构的补救计划迫在眉睫，巴克莱银行对汽车金融裁决提出质疑</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/barclays-challenges-motor-finance-ruling-uk-watchdogs-redress-scheme-looms-2024-10-15/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴克莱银行周二请求伦敦高等法院推翻对汽车金融委员会的一项重要裁决，该案件预计将影响英国金融监管机构可能提出的价值超过 10 亿英镑的消费者赔偿计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/barclays-challenges-motor-finance-ruling-uk-watchdogs-redress-scheme-looms-2024-10-15/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 10:45:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
