      <title>能源、矿业股拖累欧洲 STOXX 600 指数从两周高点回落</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/european-shares-climb-two-week-highs-oil-stocks-slump-2024-10-15/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受矿业和能源股拖累，欧洲股市周二早些时候触及两周多高点后转而走低，投资者还在关注企业财报季和本周晚些时候公布的央行利率决定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/european-shares-climb-two-week-highs-oil-stocks-slump-2024-10-15/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 07:34:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
