      <title>瑞士监管机构要求瑞银加强应急计划</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/swiss-regulator-tells-ubs-strengthen-its-emergency-plans-2024-10-15/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[监管机构表示，瑞银收购瑞士信贷后必须改进其应急和恢复计划，以确保其能够在不危及金融稳定的情况下进行清盘或出售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/swiss-regulator-tells-ubs-strengthen-its-emergency-plans-2024-10-15/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 07:19:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
